<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item label</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Do you want to use the plentymarkets app to print item labels? Choose the item label that you’ve designed for this purpose.<br>
<strong><em>Tip:</em></strong> This area is only displayed if you’ve <a href="/en/app/installation#2050">linked the app to plentyBase</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Printer</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Do you want to use the plentymarkets app to print item labels? Select whichever printer you want to use for printing labels.<br>
<strong><em>Tip:</em></strong> This area is only displayed if you’ve <a href="/en/app/installation#2050">linked the app to plentyBase</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
