<h3 id="700">2.2. Searching for customers</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the customer search and access your entire customer database.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Searching for customers:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p><a href="/en/app/installation#1100">Log into the plentymarkets app</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on the menu icon (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-bars  "></i></span>) in the top left corner of the app.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-address-card-o  "></i></span> <strong>Customer search</strong>.<br>
→ The customer search opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a search criteria, e.g. a contact ID.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on <span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span> <strong>Search</strong>.<br>
→ You’ll see all the customer data records that were found.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on a customer data record.<br>
→ The detailed view is shown.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
