<h2 id="800">3. Order search</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The plentymarkets app includes an order search function, which is described on this page. First, <a href="/en/app/functions/item-search#900">configure a few basic settings</a> and decide what you want the search results to look like. These settings will go into effect when you <a href="/en/app/functions/item-search#1000">search for orders</a> later.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="900">3.1. Customising the order search</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>How many search results do you want to see at once? Should some pieces of information be displayed in large or small font?
You’ll answer these sorts of questions while customising the default search settings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Customising the order search:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p><a href="/en/app/installation#1100">Log into the plentymarkets app</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on the menu icon (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-bars  "></i></span>) in the top left corner of the app.</p>
</li>
