<p>Tap on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-list-alt  "></i></span> <strong>Orders</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Note <a href="#table-modify-order-search">Table 3</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap on the check mark (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-check  "></i></span>) in the upper right corner to confirm the change.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
