<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">What should the order data look like? The plentymarkets app comes with a default template, which is appropriate for most order searches. However, you can create <a href="/en/app/installation#1900">additional templates</a> in the plentymarkets backend menu <strong>Setup » plenty app » Order overview</strong> and then select these templates from the drop-down list here.<br>
