But maybe you want to regularly search for orders that are in a specific status or that came from a specific sales platform.
Not only can you <a href="/en/app/functions/item-search#1100">use filters to narrow down the search results</a>, but you can also save your most frequently used search criteria so you don’t have to re-enter the filter parameters every time you search.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1000">3.2. Searching for orders</h3>
